metadata.name: Smile Candy
metadata.description:
Opened the jar of candies, 
Found it to be a jar of smiles.  
With a smile from the heart  
Pouring joy all around,  
Spreading smiles to all  
Like a sweet candy to have :-) 


Artist: Roshna Roy  
Collection: GM Tales  
Edition: 1/1  
Collection Size: 50  
Year Created: 2022
